ore need to split the bill! Want to invite someone? Place their orders through your app.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1494627019858{margin-bottom: 40px !important;}\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\"bounceInLeft\"]<img class=\"alignleft wp-image-42 size-thumbnail\" src=\"//localhost:3000/app/uploads/2017/05/Wrong-150x150.png\" alt=\"No Wrong Orders\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /><strong>No Order Missed</strong>\r\nWaitrr orders pop-up immediately at the bar or in the kitchen. Orders are always done by you, so you\'ll always get exactly what you ordered![/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\"bounceInRight\"]<strong><img class=\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-41\" src=\"//localhost:3000/app/uploads/2017/05/Time-150x150.png\" alt=\"More personal time\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" />\r\nMore Personal Time</strong>\r\nDon\'t waste time trying to get the attenton of the staff. Order and pay all on your mobile phone, and spend more time with your loved ones![/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" css=\".vc_custom_1494624305419{padding-top: 40px !important;padding-bottom: 40px !important;background-color: #7bd1e9 !important;}\"][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center; color: #fff;\">AS FEATURED IN:</h3>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\" css=\".vc_custom_1494626867137{margin-bottom: 40px !important;}\"][vc_single_image image=\"44\" img_size=\"medium\" alignment=\"center\" css_animation=\"rollIn\" css=\".vc_custom_1494626428285{margin-bottom: 20px !important;}\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\" css=\".vc_custom_1494626872034{margin-bottom: 40px !important;}\"][vc_single_image image=\"45\" img_size=\"medium\" alignment=\"center\" css_animation=\"rollIn\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3