nceInLeft\"]<strong>\r\n<img class=\"alignleft wp-image-159 size-thumbnail\" src=\"https://waitrr.com/app/uploads/2017/05/Efficiency-1-150x150.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" />Maximize Operational Efficiency</strong>\r\nReceive orders directly from your customers, and streamline your workflow! Let your staff focus on efficiently preparing and serving orders![/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1494626935428{margin-bottom: 30px !important;}\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\"bounceInRight\"]<strong>\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-160 size-thumbnail alignleft\" src=\"https://waitrr.com/app/uploads/2017/05/Service-1-150x150.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" />Improve Customer Service</strong>\r\nLess time spent taking orders and settling payments means your staff can spend their time providing your customers with amazing service![/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1494626942749{margin-bottom: 30px !important;}\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\"bounceInLeft\"]<img class=\"wp-image-161 size-thumbnail alignleft\" src=\"https://waitrr.com/app/uploads/2017/05/Dropoff-1-150x150.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /><strong>Reduce Drop-off Rates</strong>\r\nLet your customers skip the queue by allowing them to order from anywhere for pick up at their desired time. Help them save time![/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1494627012479{margin-bottom: 30px !important;}\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\"bounceInRight\" css=\".vc_custom_1496811749161{margin-bottom: 30px !important;}\"]<img class=\"alignleft wp-image-162 size-thumbnail\" src=\"https://waitrr.com/app/uploads/2017/05/Revenue-1-150x150.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /><strong>Increase Revenue</strong>\r\nCustomers spend 30% more on mobile. Increase your revenue by allowing your customers to easily order and pay on their mobile phones.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1494627019858{margin-bottom: 40px !important;}\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\"bounceInLeft\"]<img class=\"alignleft wp-image-163 size-thumbnail\" src=\"https://waitrr.com/app/uploads/2017/05/24hrs-150x150.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /><strong>Quick &amp; Simple Set-up</strong>\r\nKeen on signing up with Waitrr? Provide us with the materials we need, and Waitrr can go live at your restaurant in as fast as one day![/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\"bounceInRight\"]<strong><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-164 size-thumbnail\" src=\"https://waitrr.com/app/uploads/2017/05/Updates-1-150x150.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" />Regular Updates</strong>\r\nWaitrr is constantly working hard to bring improvements and new features to make your lives easier and more efficient — at no extra cost![/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_id=\"testimonials\" css=\".vc_custom_1494628802418{padding-top: 40px !important;padding-bottom: 40px !important;}\"][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">TESTIMONIALS</h2>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][vc_single_image image=\"176\" img_size=\"200x200\" alignment=\"center\" css_animation=\"flipInX\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\"flipInX\"]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>“Getting manpower is the biggest issue faced by the F&amp;B sector in Singapore. It takes months to hire staff. We also face a high turnover rate. <span style=\"color: #28b4da;\"><strong>With Waitrr, </strong></span><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #28b4da;\">I get to save at least five staff members and $10,000 in monthly wages</span></strong>.</span>”</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Jam Ignite, Founder</strong>\r\n<strong>I Am Cafe</strong></p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][vc_single_image image=\"177\" img_size=\"200x200\" alignment=\"center\" css_animation=\"flipInX\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\"flipInX\"]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>“<span style=\"color: #28b4da;\"><strong>The best way to manage a busy restaurant with less staff is to get Waitrr.</strong></span> With Waitrr, your staff can skip the order taking and payments part, and make small talk with your customers for a better restaurant experience. If there\'s an app that you need... It\'s Waitrr – their support team is the best!”</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Jan Verrdan Antonio, General Manager</strong>\r\n<strong>Food on Fire</strong></p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][vc_single_image image=\"178\" img_size=\"200x200\" alignment=\"center\" css_animation=\"flipInX\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\"flipInX\"]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>“Your cashiers can only do that much in terms of taking orders. They have to balance speed and customer service, which usually isn\'t easy especially if you have a large crowd at a fast pace. <span style=\"color: #28b4da;\"><strong>With Waitrr, people in a rush can still have a pleasant experience at your shop instead of giving up queuing altogether.</strong></span>”</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Jake Pang, </strong><strong>Managing Director\r\n</strong><strong>Wafuken</strong></p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" css=\".vc_custom_1494624305419{padding-top: 40px !important;padding-bottom: 40px !important;background-color: #7bd1e9 !important;}\"][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center; color: #fff;\">AS FEATURED IN:</h3>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\" css=\".vc_custom_1494626867137{margin-botto