: 40px !important;padding-bottom: 60px !important;background-color: #eeeeee !important;}\"][vc_column 0=\"\"][vc_column_text 0=\"\"]\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">BENEFITS</h2>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner 0=\"\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1494626929932{margin-bottom: 30px !important;}\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\"bounceInLeft\"]<img class=\"alignleft wp-image-39 size-thumbnail\" src=\"//localhost:3000/app/uploads/2017/05/Free-150x150.png\" alt=\"Free\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /><strong>Completely Free</strong>\r\nWaitrr is completely free of charge. No fees or additional charges, no price markups, no wallet to top up. Convenience, right in your hands![/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1494626935428{margin-bottom: 30px !important;}\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\"bounceInRight\"]<img class=\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-40\" src=\"//localhost:3000/app/uploads/2017/05/Taps-150x150.png\" alt=\"Order in Seconds\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /><strong>Order in Seconds</strong>\r\nOrdering your favourite meal or drink takes seconds. Simply browse the menu, select your orders, and confirm. Done. It\'s that easy![/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner 0=\"\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1494626942749{margin-bottom: 30px !important;}\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\"bounceInLeft\"]<strong><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-38 size-thumbnail\" src=\"//localhost:3000/app/uploads/2017/05/Cashless-150x150.png\" alt=\"Cashless\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" />Cashless Payment</strong>\r\nYou don\'t need cash to use Waitrr. Pay through the app with your credit card or PayPal account. We’ll send you the receipt by email.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1494627012479{margin-bottom: 30px !important;}\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\"bounceInRight\" css=\".vc_custom_1496743179500{margin-bottom: 30px !important;}\"]<strong><img class=\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-37\" src=\"//localhost:3000/app/uploads/2017/05/Bill-150x150.png\" alt=\"No Hassle\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" />No Hassle</strong>\r\nSplitting bills can be annoying and lengthy. With Waitrr you pay only for your order so no more need to split the bill! Want to invite someone? Place their orders through your app.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner 0=\"\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1494627019858{margin-bottom: 40px !important;}\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\"bounceInLeft\"]<img class=\"alignleft wp-image-42 size-thumbnail\" src=\"//localhost:3000/app/uploads/2017/05/Wrong-150x150.png\" alt=\"No Wrong Orders\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /><strong>No Order Missed</strong>\r\nWaitrr orders pop-up immediately at the bar or in the kitchen. Orders are always done by you, so you\'ll always get exactly what you ordered![/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\"bounceInRight\"]<strong><img class=\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-41\" src=\"//localhost:3000/app/uploads/2017/05/Time-150x150.png\" alt=\"More personal time\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" />More Personal Time</strong>\r\nDon\'t waste time trying to get the attention of the staff. Order and pay all on your mobile phone, and spend more time with your loved ones![/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" css=\".vc_custom_1494624305419{padding-top: 40px !important;padding-bottom: 40px !important;background-color: #7bd1e9 !important;}\"][vc_column 0=\"\"][vc_column_text 0=\"\"]\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center; color: #fff;\">AS FEATURED IN:</h3>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner 0=\"\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\" css=\".vc_custom_1494626867137{margin-bottom: 40px !important;}\"][vc_single_image image=\"44\" img_size=\"medium\" alignment=\"center\" onclick=\"custom_link\" img_link_target=\"_blank\" css_animation=\"rollIn\" css=\".vc_custom_1496246789886{margin-bottom: 20px !important;}\" link=\"http://www.beritaharian.sg/setempat/kafe-guna-app-untuk-jimat\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\" css=\".vc_custom_1494626872034{margin-bottom: 40px !important;}\"][vc_single_image image=\"130\" img_size=\"medium\" alignment=\"center\" onclick=\"custom_link\" img_link_target=\"_blank\" css_animation=\"rollIn\" link=\"http://holeinthewall.sg/2017/03/07/i-am-cafe-tampines-hub/\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\"][vc_single_image image=\"46\" img_size=\"medium\" alignment=\"center\" onclick=\"custom_link\" img_link_target=\"_blank\" css_animation=\"rollIn\" link=\"https://vulcanpost.com/609188/waitrr-app-singapore-startup/\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row]',	'Users',	'',	'inherit',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'2-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2017-12-04 16:12:17',	'2017-12-04 08:12:17',	'',	2,	'https://waitrr.com/2-revision-v1/',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
(331,	8,	'2017-12-05 19:30:40',	'2017-12-05 11:30:40',	'Salads have always been a staple when it comes to eating healthy or losing weight. Recently, they’ve really come to the fore with a whole host of funky superfood options and are often drenched in dressing to compensate for the bland taste of uncooked vegetables. Here, we display an awesome range of Singapore’s top salad bars and their famous offerings that not only taste great but look amazing! We’re not only about Caesar salads now. Here are our top picks of the most outrageous yet healthy salads in Singapore worthy of your Instagram feed.\n<h3>Guac and Go</h3>\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-276 size-full\" src=\"https://waitrr.com/app/uploads/2017/11/Guac-and-Go-Instagrammable-Salads.jpg\" alt=\"Guac and Go Instagrammable Salads\" width=\"775\" height=\"541\" />\n\nGuac and Go - their speciality is in the name. With all sorts of weird, wonderful and downright crazy offerings, their cuisine packs a serious healthy punch. With tons of options ranging from smoothie bowls packed with superfood berries and granola to a diverse selection of salads, Guac and Go is a surefire option for healthy eaters. One of their signatures ia a bowl of sweet potato with well-seasoned chicken, tofu, lentils and tomatoes with salsa and tons of greens with a fresh scoop of guacamole.\n\nAddress : 32 Maxwell Road #01-08 069115 Singapore\nOpening Hours : 10:00 AM - 6:00 PM\nFacebook page : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pg/guacngo\">https://www.facebook.com/pg/guacngo</a>\n<h3>The Daily Cut</h3>\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-284 size-full\" src=\"https://waitrr.com/app/uploads/2017/11/The-Daily-Cut-Instagrammable-Salads.jpg\" alt=\"The Daily Cut Instagrammable Salads\" width=\"750\" />\n\nWith so many juicy superfood offerings on their menu, The Daily Cut certainly makes the cut! They offer superfood bowls, super low carb high-fiber dishes and more greens than you can shake a stick at. In addition, they have excellent offerings of fresh fish - nourishing! Make a selection and tuck-in!\n\nFacebook page : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/thedailycut.sg/\">https://www.facebook.com/thedailycut.sg/</a>\n<h3>The Green Bar</h3>\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-274 size-full\" src=\"https://waitrr.com/app/uploads/2017/11/Green-Bar-Instagrammable-Salad.jpg\" alt=\"Green Bar Instagrammable Salad\" width=\"750\" />\n\nThe Green Bar always comes up in top 10s and top 5s. It lives up to its name, green, healthy, juicy and extensive offerings of super healthy food make up its menus. Amongst its huge selections of custom crafted salads formed with high-quality ingredients there are two standout dishes, The Smoked Duck Surprise and the Tandoor Tandoor.\n\nAddress : Millenia Walk, 9 Raffles Boulevard, #01-91039596 Singapore\nOpening Hours : 8:30am - 9pm\nFacebook :<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/TheGreenBar\"> https://www.facebook.com/TheGreenBar</a>\n<h3>Green Croft</h3>\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-275 size-full\" src=\"https://waitrr.com/app/uploads/2017/11/Green-Croft-Instagrammable-Salad.jpg\" alt=\"Green Croft Instagrammable Salad\" width=\"750\" />\n\nThe Green Croft serves a divine range of salads that are sure to re-energise you to epic proportions whenever you go there to eat. With fresh ingredients that span all your usual suspects all the way to cutting edge superfoods, it weighs in as one of the most diverse salad bars in the area. They’ve got a few signatures that make great use of high quality seafood, all crafted with super healthy eating at its heart.\n\nAddress : 18 Tai Seng, 18 Tai Seng Street, #01-K2, Singapore, 539775\nFacebook : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/GreenCroft.SG/\">https://www.facebook.com/GreenCroft.SG/</a>\n<h3>Raw Bar</h3>\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-332 size-full\" src=\"https://waitrr.com/app/uploads/2017/11/Rawbar_2.png\" alt=\"Raw Bar Salad\" width=\"821\" height=\"549\" />\n\nRaw bar lives up to its namesake. It serves rawly healthy salads - no health compromises and tons of tasty flavours. Bursting with choice, Raw Bar packs amazing signature wraps into their diverse set of juicy offerings. Perfect for any time of day! With tons of top ingredients in stock, Raw Bar makes the most out of its precisely organised menu.\n\nAddress : 9 Raffles Place, #B1-08 Republic Plaza, Singapore 048619\nOpening Hours : 9:00AM - 7:00PM\nFacebook page : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RawBarSingapore/\">https://www.facebook.com/RawBarSingapore/</a>\n<h3>Shinkansen</h3>\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-281\" src=\"https://waitrr.com/app/uploads/2017/11/Shinkansen-Salad-300x219.jpg\" alt=\"Shinkansen Salad\" width=\"750\" />\n\nShinkansen’s beautifully presented foods are divine in both their quality and their healthy features. Under a new concept brand, ‘Salmon Samurai’, they seek to provide the highest quality freshest fish to their loyal customers. Packing tons of signature fish dishes as well as Japanese style protein bowls which are packed with super healthy food zen for any time of day.\n\nAddress : Ocean Financial Centre B1-08 at Raffles Place 100AM #03-22 at 100 Tras Street\nFacebook page : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/shinkanseneats/\">https://www.facebook.com/shinkanseneats/</a>\n<h3>Saladstop!</h3>\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-280\" src=\"https://waitrr.com/app/uploads/2017/11/SaladStop-instagrammable-salad-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"SaladStop instagrammable salad\" width=\"750\" />\n\nSaladstop! Is a really popular salad bar which has 10 outlets over Singapore. They really pull crowds to their massive selection of signature salads, wraps and fresh ingredients that are pooled into their amazingly diverse dishes. Some offerings to try are their huge wraps and soup, notably their roasted pumpkin soup.\n\nFacebook page : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/SaladStop/\">https://www.facebook.com/SaladStop/</a>\n<h3>Lean Bento</h3>\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-278\" src=\"https://waitrr.com/app/uploads/2017/11/Lean-Bistro-Instagrammable-Salad-300x183.jpg\" alt=\"Lean Bento Instagrammable Salad\" width=\"750\" />\n\nLean Bento focuses on clean, high protein eating. Their diverse range of superfood charged salads and mains provides tons of healthy additions. Excellent mains accompany their vast salad offerings and together, they make Lean Bento a real treat for any meal time. Many people cite their salmon salads are top notch.\n\nAddress : 43 Holland Drive Singapore\nFacebook page : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/leanbentocom/\">https://www.facebook.com/leanbentocom/</a>\n<h3>The Poke Shack</h3>\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-286\" src=\"https://waitrr.com/app/uploads/2017/11/The-Poke-Shack-Instagrammable-Salad-269x300.jpg\" alt=\"The Poke Shack Instagrammable Salad\" width=\"750\" />\n\nFrom superfood loaded bowls to salads charged with top healthy ingredients, The Poke Shack provides sweets to savouries with all manner of salads to boot. Displayed here we have their top notch wasabi mayo salmon poke with kale salad - totally loaded with things that make you go mmmmmm!\n\nAddress : 12 Marina Blvd, 02-09 MBFC Tower 3 018982 Singapore\nFacebook page : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/thepokeshack.sg/\">https://www.facebook.com/thepokeshack.sg/</a>\n<h3>Sarnies</h3>\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-295\" src=\"https://waitrr.com/app/uploads/2017/11/Sarnies-Instaworthy-Salad-300x205.jpg\" alt=\"Sarnies Instaworthy Salad\" width=\"750\" />\n\nSarnies’ menu is jam packed with great quality food. They have a wide array of internationally themed salads that draw inspiration from classic dishes. Crafting their salads with a plethora of quality superfoods like pomegranate, shallots and nuts of various types, they’re sure to offer something for any inspired healthy eater.\n\nAddress : 136 Telok Ayer Street, Singapore 068601\nOpening Hours : 7:30AM - 12:00PM\nFacebook page : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sarnies.sin