ngredients at high-speed on a bed of porridge so zhap percolates slowly into it. More meats and seafood steamed for your porridge = a better flavour, simple! Amongst their awesome Dim Sum dishes are these glorious Lotus Paste Bear Buns. It’s a fairly smart restaurant and the fact they steam your meat over rice means your rice-like porridge is both healthy and tasty by the time you come to eat it. Original and tasty!\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Address: 68 Serangoon Garden Way, Singapore 555962</li>\r\n 	<li>Opening hours: Tue-Fri 11am to 3pm, 6pm to 11pm, Sat-Sun 11:30am to 11pm</li>\r\n 	<li>Tel: 6281 6939</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Majestic Bay</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-364 size-full\" src=\"https://waitrr.com/app/uploads/2017/12/Majestic-Bay.png\" alt=\"Majestic Bay\" width=\"697\" height=\"522\" />\r\n\r\nMajestic Bay features a rather classy environment which juxtaposes nicely with its cute Dim Sum. There’s tons of colourful offerings which look stunning and taste delicious. The arty designs of Dim Sum never cease to amaze and here, you can look towards the amazing yellow ducklings filled with Nutella and yams. They’re delightful and they really do look awesome! On top of all these Dim Sum offerings are loads of great seafood dishes including Asia Mud Crabs or US Dungeness Crabs - tasty!\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Address: 18 Marina Gardens Drive, #01-10, Below Flower Dome, Gardens By The Bay, Singapore 018953</li>\r\n 	<li>Opening hours: Mon-Sun 11:30am to 3pm, 5:45pm to 9pm</li>\r\n 	<li>Tel: 6604 6604</li>\r\n</ul>',	'Cute Must-Try Dim Sum Dishes in Singapore',	'',	'inherit',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'358-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2017-12-19 14:57:09',	'2017-12-19 06:57:09',	'',	358,	'https://waitrr.com/358-revision-v1/',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
