/div>\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n<h3>Hungry Heroes</h3>\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_456\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"800\"]<img class=\"img-responsive wp-image-456 size-full\" src=\"https://waitrr.com/app/uploads/2018/01/Hungry-Heroes-1.jpg\" alt=\"Hungry Heroes Cafe\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" /> Photo Source: https://sethlui.com[/caption]\r\n\r\nHungry Heroes is an awesome superhero themed cafe adorned with all manner of film memorabilia from superhero films throughout the ages. The restaurant specializes in delicious meat cuts and chips. Quirky and tasty! Hungry Heroes is perfect for film lovers and film discussions are held often.\r\n<div class=\"_eFb\">\r\n<div class=\"_mr kno-fb-ctx\" data-dtype=\"d3adr\" data-local-attribute=\"d3adr\" data-ved=\"0ahUKEwibqJmFh__YAhWMLY8KHTcCCD8QghwIpgEoADAV\"><span class=\"_xdb\">Address: </span><span class=\"_Xbe\">33 Tessensohn Rd, Singapore 217656</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n<h3>Central P.E.R.K</h3>\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_457\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"1488\"]<img class=\"img-responsive wp-image-457 size-full\" src=\"https://waitrr.com/app/uploads/2018/01/Central-Perk-SG.png\" alt=\"Central Perk SG\" width=\"1488\" height=\"843\" /> Photo Source: http://www.centralperk.sg/[/caption]\r\n\r\nIf you love the US sitcom friends then you’ll recognise some features of this quirky cafe. You can find replica pieces from the famous hit TV show and enjoy yourself like Joey, Phoebe, Chandler and co in this quirky central cafe. With a real american theme, this cafe is sure to satisfy any lover of unique cafe spaces.\r\n<div class=\"_eFb\">\r\n<div class=\"_mr kno-fb-ctx\" data-dtype=\"d3adr\" data-local-attribute=\"d3adr\" data-ved=\"0ahUKEwiM88eRh__YAhUIo48KHbLjBOsQghwIvQEoADAU\"><span class=\"_xdb\">Address: </span><span class=\"_Xbe\">1 Magazine Road, Central Mall #01-01, Singapore 059567</span></div>\r\n<h3 class=\"_mr kno-fb-ctx\" data-dtype=\"d3adr\" data-local-attribute=\"d3adr\" data-ved=\"0ahUKEwiM88eRh__YAhUIo48KHbLjBOsQghwIvQEoADAU\"></h3>\r\n<h3 class=\"_mr kno-fb-ctx\" data-dtype=\"d3adr\" data-local-attribute=\"d3adr\" data-ved=\"0ahUKEwiM88eRh__YAhUIo48KHbLjBOsQghwIvQEoADAU\">Grassroots Book Room</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_458\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"1104\"]<img class=\"img-responsive wp-image-458 size-full\" src=\"https://waitrr.com/app/uploads/2018/01/Grassroots-Book-Room.png\" alt=\"Grassroots Book Room\" width=\"1104\" height=\"781\" /> Photo Source: https://www.facebook.com/grassrootsbookroom/[/caption]\r\n\r\nThis book safe is simple, elegant and plainly unpretentious. There’s no super-trendy vibe here and that’s attractive and heaps of cool in itself. The books are well stocked, well chosen and range from classic pieces of literature to popular modern books.\r\n<div class=\"_eFb\">\r\n<div class=\"_mr kno-fb-ctx\" data-dtype=\"d3adr\" data-local-attribute=\"d3adr\" data-ved=\"0ahUKEwjNjaSnh__YAhXMq48KHXZWDfQQghwIogEoADAU\"><span class=\"_xdb\">Address: </span><span class=\"_Xbe\">25 Bukit Pasoh Rd, Singapore 089839</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n<h3>Look See Look See</h3>\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_459\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"1500\"]<img class=\"size-full wp-image-459\" src=\"https://waitrr.com/app/uploads/2018/01/Looksee_Facade.jpg\" alt=\"Looksee\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1269\" /> Photo Source: http://www.lobehold.com/looksee/[/caption]\r\n\r\nLocated in the Beach Road shophouse, this lovely little reading room serves a wondrous range of special teas. There are rows and rows of interesting books dispersed throughout the premises. A true space for that all important relaxation and rejuvenation, Look See Look See is a must-visit cafe\r\n<div class=\"_eFb\">\r\n<div class=\"_mr kno-fb-ctx\" data-dtype=\"d3adr\" data-local-attribute=\"d3adr\" data-ved=\"0ahUKEwjL06mzh__YAhXGQY8KHTnZCRsQghwInwEoADAU\"><span class=\"_xdb\">Address: </span><span class=\"_Xbe\">267 Beach Rd, Singapore 199545</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n