om/OriginalSinRestaurant/ </a>\r\n<h3>Jamie’s Italian</h3>\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_487\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"764\"]<img class=\"img-responsive wp-image-487 size-full\" src=\"https://waitrr.com/app/uploads/2018/02/Jamies-Italian.png\" alt=\"7 Hottest Vegetarian Fine Dining Restaurants in Singapore\" width=\"764\" height=\"571\" /> Photo Source: https://www.jamieoliver.com/italian/singapore/menu/[/caption]\r\n\r\nJamie Oliver is an internationally renowned chef who campaigns actively for healthy eating options all over the world. This Italian is not a pure vegetarian restaurant. However, Jamie’s focus on healthy eating ensures that the menu is generous with vegetarian dishes.\r\n\r\nThe restaurant itself is delightfully designed with classic chic Italian decor. Terracotta floors and antiques top off the classic Italian decor.\r\n\r\nOut of the many options on show, the Classic Superfood Salad really hits the mark, providing an awesomely healthy and extremely tasty choice for veggies. It\'s vegetarian fine dining menu features tons of ingredients including lentils, quinoa, mint, beets and rice dressed in vinegar. That’s not it though! It also contains avocados, broccoli, pomegranate and seeds.\r\n\r\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/jamiesitaliansingapore/\">https://www.facebook.com/jamiesitaliansingapore/ </a>',	'7 Hottest Vegetarian Fine Dining Restaurants in Singapore',	'',	'inherit',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'471-autosave-v1',	'',	'',	'2018-02-20 16:52:06',	'2018-02-20 08:52:06',	'',	471,	'https://waitrr.com/471-autosave-v1/',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
