(528,	8,	'2018-03-16 12:36:48',	'2018-03-16 04:36:48',	'Cheesecakes will always have a special place in the stomachs of many. Despite their obvious calorific characteristics, even when compared to other desserts, cheesecakes have an immortal place in the dessert menu of restaurants and cafes. And in Singapore, we\'ve definitely got a whole list of best cheesecakes in Singapore to try!\r\n\r\nWhether it’s the gooey goodness, the chocolatey velvetyness or the decadent juiciness, people are rightly obsessed with cheesecakes. The best result of this obsession? There are more types of cheesecake available than you can imagine.\r\n\r\nCheesecakes come in many shapes, sizes and flavours. Here\'s our list of best cheesecakes in Singapore.\r\n<h3>Cat &amp; The Fiddle Cakes</h3>\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_532\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"777\"]<img class=\"img-responsive wp-image-532 size-full\" src=\"https://waitrr.com/app/uploads/2018/03/cat-and-fiddle-cakes.png\" alt=\"7 Best Creamiest Buttery Cheesecakes in Singapore\" width=\"777\" height=\"519\" /> Image Source: http://www.makansutra.com/stories/1/1148/TheCakewithCheesyStories[/caption]\r\n\r\nThis online cake shop was founded by the prolific chef Daniel Tay. Previously, he was the founder of Bakerzinn and was also a confectionary chef at the rather famous French Restaurant Les Amis. This shop specializes in, guess what? Cheesecakes..! There are so many flavours available - it’s quite astounding!\r\n\r\nSome, like the Maneki Neko cheesecake (Yuzu, lemon and lime), are light and refreshing. Others, like the Modern Duke’s Pudding cheesecake are rich and decadent.\r\n\r\nCan’t choose? Then maybe try them all! The Fickle Feline box contains 10 mixed flavours!\r\n\r\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/catthefiddle/\">https://www.facebook.com/catthefiddle/</a>\r\n<h3>LeTAO</h3>\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_533\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"871\"]<img class=\"img-responsive wp-image-533 size-full\" src=\"https://waitrr.com/app/uploads/2018/03/letao.png\" alt=\"letao cheesecakes\" width=\"871\" height=\"576\" /> Image Source: http://danielfooddiary.com/2016/11/28/letaosg/[/caption]\r\n\r\nLeTAO specializes in Japanese style cheesecakes. They’re created with premier ingredients - the real cream of the crop!\r\n\r\nSome, like the Double Fromage cheesecake are made from mascarpone sourced from the Italian cheese producer Ambrosi. This specialist cheese is imported from Lombardy and is infused with fresh cream and other ingredients for a real, authentic cheesecake experience.\r\n\r\nFor a more chocolatey choice, the Double Chocolat cheesecake uses extremely decadent chocolate for a real indulgent treat.\r\nLeTAO fuse classic cheesecakes with modern takes on the dessert. Some of them are pretty cheesy rather than sweet, so if you really love that sumptuous cheesy taste then this is the place to head.\r\n\r\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/catthefiddle/\">https://www.facebook.com/catthefiddle/</a>\r\n<h3>Chezcake Bistro</h3>\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_534\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"900\"]<img class=\"img-responsive wp-image-534 size-full\" src=\"https://waitrr.com/app/uploads/2018/03/chezcake-bistro.png\" alt=\"7 Best Creamiest Buttery Cheesecakes in Singapore\" width=\"900\" height=\"600\" /> Image Source : http://www.chezcakebistro.com.sg/home/70-double-decker-cheesecake.html[/caption]\r\n\r\nThis little cafe doesn’t just serve cheesecake but as the name suggests, they’re pretty specialist in this area. Alongside pizzas, burgers and other mains is a star-studded array of cheesy goodness.\r\n\r\nThe cheesecakes as Chezcake Bistro are prepared gloriously with fresh ingredients and there are tons of options on offer. They’re pretty focused on maintaining a level of health amongst their desserts so if you’re watching your waistline then don’t be scared!\r\n\r\nStill, there are all the classics available - New York Cheesecake, Creme Brulee Cheesecake and all sorts ranging from white chocolate cheesecakes to rum and raisin, Pulut Hitam..the list goes on!\r\n\r\nAside from these are more bespoke offerings like the Green Tea and Red Bean cheesecake. From classic to outrageous Chezcake Bistro brings out the best in cheesecakes.\r\n\r\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/chezcake.bistro/\">https://www.facebook.com/chezcake.bistro/</a>\r\n<h3>Cake Spade</h3>\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_535\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"973\"]<img class=\"img-responsive wp-image-535 size-full\" src=\"https://waitrr.com/app/uploads/2018/03/cakespade.png\" alt=\"7 Best Creamiest Buttery Cheesecakes in Singapore\" width=\"973\" height=\"573\" /> Image Source: http://www.cheersonic.com/strawberry-tofu-cheesecake-cutting-machine/[/caption]\r\n\r\nThis patisserie is set in a lovely pink cafe and its cheesecakes come in every colour of the rainbow. Amongst the offerings are lots of healthy, lighter options. These are prepared with fresh fruit and other delightfully healthy ingredients - they’re free from artificial ingredients and preservatives. One famous offering is the Strawberry Tofu Cheesecake. With a super-light and creamy interior and fresh strawberry topping, this cheesecake won’t break your diet completely!\r\n\r\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cakespadesg/\">https://www.facebook.com/cakespadesg/</a>\r\n<h3>TheJellyHearts</h3>\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_536\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"867\"]<img class=\"img-responsive wp-image-536 size-full\" src=\"https://waitrr.com/app/uploads/2018/03/thejellyhearts.png\" alt=\"7 Best Creamiest Buttery Cheesecakes in Singapore\" width=\"867\" height=\"574\" /> Image Source: https://kopitiambot.com/2017/12/19/thejellyhearts-new-pandan-gula-melaka-jelly-cheese-cake-new-outlet-at-the-clementi-mall/[/caption]\r\n\r\nThis cake shop really does produce some of the most stunning cakes you can lay eyes on. Their selection is massive, too. It’s not all just eye candy though - these cakes are deliciou