tisserie.png\" alt=\"7 Best Creamiest Buttery Cheesecakes in Singapore\" width=\"739\" height=\"417\" /> Image Source: https://sg.openrice.com/en/singapore/article/singapores-must-try-cheese-creations-a700[/caption]\r\n\r\nThis stunning patisserie and cafe mixes Japanese and European cuisine with amazing results. Some of the desserts are simply stunning - they definitely fall into the ‘looks too good to eat’ category.\r\n\r\nSome of their cheesecakes, like the Mango Soufle are delicate and light but chocolate lovers, do not fear, as the Earl Grey Choco cake is a real star in this super menu of sweet-treats.\r\n\r\nFlor’s desserts are just so delicate and beautiful. Wolfing them down seems like a crime - don’t feel too guilty, though!\r\n\r\nFacebook:<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/florpatisserie/\"> https://www.facebook.com/florpatisserie/</a>',	'7 Best Cheesecakes in Singapore - Creamiest and Buttery!',	'',	'publish',	'open',	'open',	'',	'8-best-cheesecakes-in-singapore',	'',	'',	'2018-03-16 12:36:48',	'2018-03-16 04:36:48',	'',	0,	'https://waitrr.com/?p=528',	0,	'post',	'',	0),
