 40px !important;padding-bottom: 60px !important;background-color: #eeeeee !important;}\"][vc_column 0=\"\"][vc_column_text 0=\"\"]\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">BENEFITS</h2>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner 0=\"\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1494626929932{margin-bottom: 30px !important;}\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\"none\"]<img class=\"alignleft wp-image-39 size-thumbnail\" src=\"/app/uploads/2017/05/Free-150x150.png\" alt=\"Free\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /><strong>Completely Free</strong>\r\nWaitrr is completely free of charge. No fees or additional charges, no price markups, no wallet to top up. Convenience, right in your hands![/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1494626935428{margin-bottom: 30px !important;}\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\"none\"]<img class=\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-40\" src=\"/app/uploads/2017/05/Taps-150x150.png\" alt=\"Order in Seconds\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /><strong>Order in Seconds</strong>\r\nOrdering your favourite meal or drink takes seconds. Simply browse the menu, select your orders, and confirm. Done. It\'s that easy![/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner 0=\"\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1494626942749{margin-bottom: 30px !important;}\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\"none\"]<strong><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-38 size-thumbnail\" src=\"/app/uploads/2017/05/Cashless-150x150.png\" alt=\"Cashless\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" />Cashless Payment</strong>\r\nYou don\'t need cash to use Waitrr. Pay through the app with your credit card or PayPal account. We’ll send you the receipt by email.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1494627012479{margin-bottom: 30px !important;}\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\"none\" css=\".vc_custom_1515492487896{margin-bottom: 30px !important;}\"]<strong><img class=\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-37\" src=\"/app/uploads/2017/05/Bill-150x150.png\" alt=\"No Hassle\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" />No Hassle</strong>\r\nSplitting bills can be annoying and lengthy. With Waitrr you pay only for your order so no more need to split the bill! Want to invite someone? Place their orders through your app.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner 0=\"\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1494627019858{margin-bottom: 40px !important;}\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\"none\"]<img class=\"alignleft wp-image-42 size-thumbnail\" src=\"/app/uploads/2017/05/Wrong-150x150.png\" alt=\"No Wrong Orders\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /><strong>No Order Missed</strong>\r\nWaitrr orders pop-up immediately at the bar or in the kitchen. Orders are always done by you, so you\'ll always get exactly what you ordered![/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\"none\"]<strong><img class=\"alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-41\" src=\"/app/uploads/2017/05/Time-150x150.png\" alt=\"More personal time\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" />More Personal Time</strong>\r\nDon\'t waste time trying to get the attention of the staff. Order and pay all on your mobile phone, and spend more time with your loved ones![/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" css=\".vc_custom_1494624305419{padding-top: 40px !important;padding-bottom: 40px !important;background-color: #7bd1e9 !important;}\"][vc_column 0=\"\"][vc_column_text 0=\"\"]\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center; color: #fff;\">AS FEATURED IN:</h3>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner 0=\"\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\" css=\".vc_custom_1494626867137{margin-bottom: 40px !important;}\"][vc_single_image image=\"44\" img_size=\"medium\" alignment=\"center\" onclick=\"custom_link\" img_link_target=\"_blank\" css_animation=\"none\" css=\".vc_custom_1496246789886{margin-bottom: 20px !important;}\" link=\"http://www.beritahar